@abstract:
Declared intent and purpose for Awesome Nickel.
@end

## Purpose

Awesome Nickel — > A configuration language that combines the simplicity of JSON with the power of functions, types, and contracts.

## Anti-Purpose

This project is NOT:
- A fork or wrapper around another tool
- A monorepo (unless explicitly structured as one)

## If In Doubt

If you are unsure whether a change is in scope, ask.
Sensitive areas: ABI definitions, license headers, CI workflows.
